# NETWORK::NETWORK_IS_SIGNED_ONLINE

## Summary
Returns TRUE if the local player is online

## Returns
* **BOOL**

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Returns whether the game is not in offline mode.

seemed not to work for some ppl
